org.gephi.utils.collection.avl
Interface ResetableIterator

All Known Implementing Classes:
ChildrenIterator, DescendantAndSelfIterator, DescendantIterator, ParamAVLIterator, TreeIterator
public interface ResetableIterator

Interface without methods, specify an iterator can be reset and used more than once.

Iterators implementing this interface possess a setNode() or reset() method.

Mathieu Bastian
